<!-- Case Studies Page: src/pages/case-studies.astro -->
---
import Layout from '../components/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout title="Client Testimonies | IronLink Technologies">
  <section class="bg-gradient-to-br from-[#1e3c72] to-[#2a5298] text-white text-center py-20 px-6">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
      <h1 class="text-5xl font-extrabold mb-6">Results That Speak. Partnerships That Last</h1>
      <p class="text-lg text-white/80">We deliver strategic, secure solutions that drive real outcomes — because trust isn’t given, it’s earned</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="bg-white py-16 px-6">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
      <div class="bg-[#f1f6fb] p-6 rounded-xl shadow">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-[#1e3c72] mb-2">🧠 Digital Transformation for SMB</h2>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-700">"IronLink overhauled our aging network into a fully cloud-integrated infrastructure. Downtime is gone, and our team collaborates faster than ever."</p>
        <p class="text-xs text-gray-500 mt-3">— Operations Director, Regional Law Firm</p>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-[#f1f6fb] p-6 rounded-xl shadow">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-[#1e3c72] mb-2">🔐 SecOps for Financial Institutions</h2>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-700">"They brought governance clarity and configured our firewalls to meet strict compliance requirements — without slowing anything down."</p>
        <p class="text-xs text-gray-500 mt-3">— IT Manager, Credit Union</p>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-[#f1f6fb] p-6 rounded-xl shadow">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-[#1e3c72] mb-2">🚀 Infrastructure Uplift at Scale</h2>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-700">"IronLink completed our site-wide upgrade on time and under budget. They’re not vendors — they’re partners in growth."</p>
        <p class="text-xs text-gray-500 mt-3">— CIO, Manufacturing Company</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="bg-[#edf2f7] py-20 px-6">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto text-center">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-[#1e3c72] mb-4">Want to See What We Can Do For You?</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6">From cybersecurity audits to complete digital overhauls, we’re trusted by organizations who can’t afford to get it wrong.</p>
      <a href="/contact" class="bg-[#1e3c72] text-white font-semibold py-3 px-6 rounded hover:bg-[#2a5298] transition">Start Your Story With Us</a>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
